    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NOTE! This is an In-Development Early version of the game, if you have issues with the game you can leave a bug report in Discord or feedback with the in-game form.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/7bd74474b8aee3a4d92afdae5b201bbe.poster.avif?t=1763700583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/7bd74474b8aee3a4d92afdae5b201bbe.webm?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/7bd74474b8aee3a4d92afdae5b201bbe.mp4?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TAME RIDABLE PETS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tame any animal with the lasso mini-game to gain a companion that you can level-up, ride into battle, and fight along-side! They even have elemental pet abilities...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/398d25caa099c1909c93561ad6987526.poster.avif?t=1763700583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/398d25caa099c1909c93561ad6987526.webm?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/398d25caa099c1909c93561ad6987526.mp4?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE INFINITE BIOMES</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an endless procedural fantasy world, discover the depth of biomes filled with living creatures, villagers, and natural features... to find all the hidden secrets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/938b6f90795caf092530a743ee6edcc2.poster.avif?t=1763700583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/938b6f90795caf092530a743ee6edcc2.webm?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/938b6f90795caf092530a743ee6edcc2.mp4?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roleplay and design your character from 5 different fantasy species, face, hair and body shapes. Then level up and specialize in your class unlocking skills in the skill tree. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/5c52a8bf87e9b6e44f81c530396b7856.poster.avif?t=1763700583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/5c52a8bf87e9b6e44f81c530396b7856.webm?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/5c52a8bf87e9b6e44f81c530396b7856.mp4?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MASTER YOUR WEAPONRY</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced dynamic combat featuring different weapon types,  dash-dodging, and a charged/mana ability system. Combat emenies with special elemental abilties and behaviors.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/102bcd76a1a63e670e57a192ec35e5f0.poster.avif?t=1763700583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/102bcd76a1a63e670e57a192ec35e5f0.webm?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/102bcd76a1a63e670e57a192ec35e5f0.mp4?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>QUEST &amp; TRADE</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main quest depicts the struggle between civilization and nature through choices that lead to different boss fights and allegiances. Eventually, these choices will impact the World of Wildaria. Villagers and bandits populate camps, villages and ruins. Converse, quest, trade, and even wager some coin in a game of Trailsweeper with the townsfolk!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/9c815be0498134af7a40b1d2727b6f7f.poster.avif?t=1763700583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/9c815be0498134af7a40b1d2727b6f7f.webm?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/9c815be0498134af7a40b1d2727b6f7f.mp4?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BATTLE GODS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve deep into procedural dungeons defend yourself from dangerous wildlife, encounter larger-than-life animal Gods, and acquire epic loot.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/00282e22e5a464e06db2a43cc122b37d.poster.avif?t=1763700583\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/00282e22e5a464e06db2a43cc122b37d.webm?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223100/extras/00282e22e5a464e06db2a43cc122b37d.mp4?t=1763700583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DISCOVER SECRETS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck finding them...  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INSPIRATIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GBA Era</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The pixel art graphics are inspired by GBA Era titles such as Zelda, Sword of Mana, Pokemon Emerald, but with modern computer-rendered shaders for a more natural wind-swept foliage and water graphics. The Gameplay is a more modern take on action-adventure RPG's from the GBA era with endless replayability lent from the procedural nature of the world, loot, and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Wildlife</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a solo game developer, maintaining self-motivation and inspiration can be challenging. I read about how Shigeru Miyamoto based the original Zelda on exploring the Japanese countryside with his father. I realized &quot;That rather than make a game like Zelda, I needed to make a game like Zelda was made.&quot; I've always loved nature- from hiking, to observing local animals or plants, to just laying in the dirt. I guarantee you will discover something new and fascinating if you just look closely and give the smallest bug or flower the time of day. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My Life Mission is to create worlds for others to explore and lose themselves in, while inspiring others to venture out into their local wildlife.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
